title: Designates state highway 19 in the town of Hume in the county of Allegany as the "Almond E. Fisher Memorial Highway"
summary: Designates state highway 19 in the town of Hume in the county of Allegany as the "Almond E. Fisher Memorial Highway".
actClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a certain portion of state highway 19 in the town of Hume in the county of Allegany as the "Almond E. Fisher Memorial Highway"
